<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ofcom> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Ofcom is the regulator and competition authority for the UK communications industries. It regulates the TV and radio sectors, fixed line telecoms, mobiles, postal services, plus the airwaves over which wireless devices operate. Ofcom works with the Department for Science, Innovation and Technology ."@en .
